stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Loading
    Loading --> DashboardReady : All data loaded
    Loading --> PartialLoad : Some widgets loaded
    PartialLoad --> DashboardReady : Remaining loaded
    DashboardReady --> Refreshing : Auto-refresh (30s)
    Refreshing --> DashboardReady : Data updated
    DashboardReady --> [*]